PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775952175
OL,3,CTalks to resume as Irish fuel protests
OL,4,Center fifth day
OL,6,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin warned that
OL,7,FIreland is on the "precipice of
OL,8,Fturning oil away from the country",
OL,9,Fdescribing the situation as
OL,10,F"unconscionable", "illogical", and
OL,11,F"difficult to comprehend".
OL,13,FThe protests, which have also seen
OL,14,Fslow-moving convoys and outright
OL,15,Fstoppages on major motorways as well
OL,16,Fas a blockade on Dublin city's main
OL,17,Fthoroughfare, began on Tuesday over
OL,18,Fthe cost of fuel.
