OL,3,CTalks to resume as Irish fuel protests
OL,4,Center fifth day
OL,6,FParticipants include professional
OL,7,Fdrivers, farmers and hauliers as well
OL,8,Fas taxi and bus operators.
OL,10,FMany official representative groups
OL,11,Frecognised by Government have
OL,12,Fexpressed sympathy with the cause but
OL,13,Fhave said they have not been involved
OL,14,Fin organising the protests.
OL,16,FGovernment ministers engaged with some
OL,17,Fof these groups on Friday but a
OL,18,Fspokesman for the protesters expressed
OL,19,F"devastation" that they were excluded
OL,20,Ffrom the meeting.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
