OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775952175
OL,3,CTalks to resume as Irish fuel protests
OL,4,Center fifth day
OL,6,FA commitment from the coalition on
OL,7,FFriday night to deliver a
OL,8,F"substantial" package of measures on
OL,9,Ffuel costs was not enough to dissuade
OL,10,Fprotesters from continuing blockades.
OL,12,FChristopher Duffy, a spokesman for the
OL,13,Fgrouping in Dublin city centre, said
OL,14,Fthe protest would continue until there
OL,15,Fwas a "serious reduction in our costs".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]wD@GOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
