OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775952175
OL,3,CTalks to resume as Irish fuel protests
OL,4,Center fifth day
OL,6,FTalks between Government departments
OL,7,Fand representative bodies are set to
OL,8,Fcontinue at lunchtime on Saturday,
OL,9,Fwith a view to finalising what deputy
OL,10,Fpremier Simon Harris said would be
OL,11,F"substantial and significant" measures
OL,12,Ffor affected industries.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, ministers said the Irish
OL,15,FDefence Forces are "on standby" to
OL,16,Fhelp the Irish police service, An
OL,17,FGarda Siochana, remove blockades at
OL,18,Fcritical infrastructure.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@]O]wD@TOUwD@_O]
