OL,3,CTalks to resume as Irish fuel protests
OL,4,Center fifth day
OL,6,FAn Garda Siochana internally declared
OL,7,Fan "exceptional event", allowing it to
OL,8,Fdesignate every member available for
OL,9,Fduty over the weekend.
